### Trend Interpretation

| Range | Assessment |
|-------|------------|
| < 5 000 ms  | Excellent — fast iteration |
| 5 000–15 000 ms | Acceptable — watch for growth |
| > 15 000 ms | Slow — investigate dependencies and monolith crates |

**Action:** If check time exceeds 15 s, profile with `cargo build --timings` and
consider splitting heavy crates.

